       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PGMINIC.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       01 WPGMNAME.
           02   PIC X(008) VALUE 'PGMCALLA'.
       01 MYMESSAGE.
           02   PIC X(100) VALUE SPACES.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.

       MAIN-LINE SECTION.

           EXEC CICS LINK
                    PROGRAM(WPGMNAME)
                    COMMAREA(MYMESSAGE)
                    LENGTH(LENGTH OF MYMESSAGE)
                    NOHANDLE
           END-EXEC.

           EXEC CICS SEND TEXT FROM(MYMESSAGE) ERASE
                    LENGTH(LENGTH OF MYMESSAGE) CURSOR(81)
           END-EXEC.

           EXEC CICS RETURN END-EXEC.
